{"tid":1029696,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"洗腦手法年輕化 rap歌唱好習","createTime":"2019-02-20T11:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T15:39:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"45041505790b78661e6da74287e2ae3b91233d65","tid":1029696,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:58:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190220/20616520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190220%2F20616520&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n8%2FBNkMLqpq56k8mIdjvCyJE%3D&h=1eb8c547\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190220%2F20616520&h=899f7e1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190220/20616520</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n洗腦手法年輕化 rap歌唱好習<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190220/large/20cj02p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190220%2Flarge%2F20cj02p.jpg&h=76d60910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有內地公司黨委稱第一時間安排黨員下載「學習強國」。<br />\n<br />\n中共近年開足馬力捧習，政策宣傳、習思想都以手機、電視深入社會每個角落。上任初期有饒舌（rap）形式、卡通形象現身的動畫短片，近期又推出電視問答節目宣傳習思想，被指圖以創新形式拉近年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n過往中共多以海報、廣告標語手法宣傳，但近年出現較輕鬆活潑的宣傳手法，如央視曾在2015年推出短片《深改小組兩歲了》，用rap形式唱好中央深化改革委員會；習近平等高層又在2013年的《領導人是怎樣煉成的》短片中，化身卡通形象，一改以往生硬的宣傳風格。<br />\n<br />\n當局去年以電視節目力銷習思想，例如央視推出《平「語」近人──習近平總書記用典》節目。湖南衞視亦播出《新時代學習大會》問答遊戲節目，問題圍繞中共政策和習近平個人經歷，節目儼如一場中共政治觀點的「背誦比賽」。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》/聯合新聞網<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：4,370萬次下載 擊敗抖音微信學「習」App 阿里開發<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n4,370萬次下載擊敗抖音微信 學「習」App阿里開發<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n聲援王全璋 大律師公會轟中共罔顧人權<br />\n<br />\n4,370萬次下載 擊敗抖音微信學「習」App 阿里開發"},{"pid":"f1f4a517ef7e227a31694b3a6e69f83bb3872abf","tid":1029696,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T12:04:36.000Z","msg":"MC jin wo<br />\nCheck it out!"},{"pid":"39ed8671625dfb0b026f625b029a588ed4140987","tid":1029696,"uid":164050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T12:24:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c73c022b587289ddb5298ce31fea8d822337f2c","tid":1029696,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T12:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/SaneHandyAmericanratsnake-max-1mb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FSaneHandyAmericanratsnake-max-1mb.gif&h=caeac1ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c327adf7a75ee76339103d58c6440d47c591ad0","tid":1029696,"uid":4493,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T12:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8bRn1Zx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8bRn1Zx.png&h=13195837&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96a0190d68395fa5062af0ff12eac5d654bee1a0","tid":1029696,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:33:20.000Z","msg":"老友，我要話聲你聽~<br />\n奶共既你真係唔係幾正~"},{"pid":"d052fdffa02505e15221ef54394057e1bd2dee22","tid":1029696,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:35:46.000Z","msg":"之前有紅薄毛語錄<br />\n今有手機習語錄<br />\n呢個國度，究竟要瘋狂到咩程度先會自我滅亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05dd66495b6825b236e7cb87b53e90a57844521f","tid":1029696,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d052fdffa02505e15221ef54394057e1bd2dee22","tid":1029696,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:35:46.000Z","msg":"之前有紅薄毛語錄<br />\n今有手機習語錄<br />\n呢個國度，究竟要瘋狂到咩程度先會自我滅亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:39:50.000Z","msg":"自相殘殺"}]}